1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,120
Do you know how to free yourself from
suffering?

2
00:00:03,920 --> 00:00:07,369
When you see things as beautiful, other
things become ugly.

3
00:00:07,369 --> 00:00:11,975
When you see things as good, other things
become bad.

4
00:00:11,975 --> 00:00:16,901
Your happiness and suffering always depend
on how you perceive the world.

5
00:00:16,901 --> 00:00:22,354
It is the view or the idea that you have
divided this world into two parts,

6
00:00:22,354 --> 00:00:23,700
beautiful and ugly.

7
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:27,244
When you are in the presence of things you
see as beautiful,

8
00:00:27,244 --> 00:00:28,689
it makes you happy.

9
00:00:28,689 --> 00:00:31,685
When you are in the presence of things you
see as ugly,

10
00:00:31,685 --> 00:00:34,040
it makes you suffer or unhappy.

11
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:39,163
You have your own liberation with you,
don't you?

12
00:00:39,163 --> 00:00:42,900
Let's begin this journey to find
unconditional happiness.
